<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>The Grid Bot - Database Editor</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;800&family=Fira+Code&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-color: #0f172a;
            --surface-color: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.7);
            --accent-color: #f97316;
            --glass-bg: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            --glass-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            --text-main: #f8fafc;
            --text-muted: #94a3b8;
            --success: #22c55e;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            background-image: 
                radial-gradient(circle at 10% 20%, rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.1), transparent 40%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 90% 80%, rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.1), transparent 40%);
            background-attachment: fixed;
            color: var(--text-main);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .navbar {
            background: var(--glass-bg);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
            padding: 16px 40px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .nav-brand {
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .nav-brand span { color: var(--accent-color); }

        .main-content {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 40px;
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        form {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            flex: 1;
        }

        textarea {
            width: 100%;
            flex: 1;
            min-height: 400px;
            background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.8);
            border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 16px;
            color: #e2e8f0;
            font-family: 'Fira Code', monospace;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            resize: vertical;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        textarea:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: var(--accent-color);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.2);
        }

        .actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 16px;
        }

        .btn {
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 14px;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .btn-success {
            background: var(--success);
            color: white;
        }

        .btn-success:hover { background: #16a34a; }

        .btn-secondary {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            color: white;
            border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2); }

        footer {
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 13px;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            border-top: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
        }
        .made-by { font-weight: 600; color: var(--accent-color); }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="nav-brand">
            🫵 the <span>grid.</span>
        </div>
        <a href="/dashboard" class="btn btn-secondary">Zurück zum Dashboard</a>
    </nav>

    <main class="main-content">
        <h1>💾 Datenbank Editor</h1>
        <p>Hier kannst du die <code>db.json</code> Datei direkt bearbeiten. Achtung: Stelle sicher, dass die Struktur im JSON-Format korrekt bleibt (sonst wird das Speichern blockiert).</p>
        
        <form action="/dashboard/db" method="POST">
            <textarea name="dbContent" spellcheck="false"><%= dbContent %></textarea>
            <div class="actions">
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-success">Speichern & Überschreiben</button>
            </div>
        </form>
    </main>

    <footer>
        made by <span class="made-by">MaxiFaxiPaxi</span>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
